| Princess Imperial of Brazil and [[Countess of Eu]] due to her marriage to [[Prince Gaston, Count of Eu|Gaston d'Orléans]]. She had 3 sons from this marriage. She also acted as [[Regent]] of the Empire while her father was traveling abroad.
