== Endnotes ==

{{notes
| refs =

{{efn
| name = Dona
| ''Dona'' is a Portuguese and Brazilian honorific added to a name which is rendered in English as ''[[Dame (title)|Dame]]'' or ''[[Lady]]'', in Italian as ''Donna'' and in Spanish as ''Doña''. Its male equivalent in Portuguese is ''[[Dom (title)|Dom]]'', in English ''[[Lord]]'' and in Spanish and Italian ''[[Don (honorific)|Don]]''.
}}

}}

